## Naming Convention

Name agents by **matching as many leading letters of the role as possible to a real human name.** Three-letter matches are better than two.

**Fixed names:** pm → **Pam**, tester → **Chester**
**Standard roles:** frontend-worker → **Freddie**, backend-worker → **Barry**, system-ops → **Sylvie**

For custom roles, follow the same leading-letters pattern. Three letters ideal, two minimum.

